@startuml
skinparam defaultFontName "WenQuanYi Zen Hei"
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor white
  BorderColor black
  FontColor black
}
skinparam package {
  BackgroundColor #F5F5F5
  BorderColor black
}
top to bottom direction

rectangle "智能旅游平台" as system #E8E8E8

rectangle "账号管理\n注册和登录、注销、个人资料管理" as account
rectangle "社交组队管理\n好友关系管理、出行小组管理、房间码加入" as social
rectangle "出行规划管理\n成员约束管理、初始方案生成、行程节点管理、地图路线导航、预算费用管理" as planning
rectangle "监测与应变管理\n事件接入管理、影响匹配分析、风险评分预警、持续动态分析、自动重规划、协同投票决策、变更记录管理、消息通知管理" as adaptive
rectangle "社区管理\n讨论区管理、攻略社区管理、攻略纳用、行后游记生成与发布" as community
rectangle "后台与监控管理\n用户管理、运营后台管理、数据统计分析" as admin

system -down-> account
system -down-> social
system -down-> planning
system -down-> adaptive
system -down-> community
system -down-> admin

account -[hidden]right-> social
social -[hidden]right-> planning
planning -[hidden]right-> adaptive
adaptive -[hidden]right-> community
community -[hidden]right-> admin
@enduml
